text: Conor Clancy (born 1971 in Kilmaley, County Clare) is a former Irish sportsperson. He played hurling with his local club Kilmaley and with the Clare senior inter-county team from 1995 until 2002. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Kilmaley hurlers Category:Clare inter-county hurlers Category:All-Ireland Senior Hurling Championship winners
